1. update ubuntu : sudo apt update

2. install gnome tweaks : sudo apt install gnome-tweaks

3. install gnome extensions : sudo apt install gnome-shell-extensions

4. download Theme : https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1241688/

5. download Icon : https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1309810/

6. download Shell : https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1220826/

7. download Wallpaper : https://4kwallpapers.com/nature/macos-catalina-mountains-island-daytime-stock-5k-188.html

8. install Snapd : sudo apt install snapd (agar perintah "snap" dapat bekerja)

9. install Slack : sudo snap install slack

10. install Spotify : sudo snap install spotify

11. install Apple Music : sudo snap install apple-music-for-linux

12. install Icloud (isinya banyak aplikasi khusus) : sudo snap install icloud-for-linux

13. install extension : Compiz alike magic lamp effect

14. install extension : Dash to dock animator

15. install extension : Desktop cube
